skdetail:

Invocation Name: daily phrases
des:
the skill searches the web for catching jargon, new words and phrases. the utterances can be
1. tell (give) me a (one) phrase
2. tell (give) me some phrases
in the 2nd case the skill will ask if the user wants to hear another one
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
